schema.label: Author Country
schema.description: The country in which a story author's Current City is located

schema.label: Story Categories & Topics
schema.description: Category & topic pairs for stories

schema.label: Engaged Categories & Topics
schema.description: Category & topic pairs for engagements

schema.label: Author Country & Region
schema.description: Country & region pairs for stories

schema.label: Parent Author Country & Region
schema.description: Country and region pairs for engagements

schema.label: Author Gender
schema.description: One of 'female', 'male', 'unknown'

schema.label: Author Education
schema.description: One of 'high_school', 'college', 'grad_school' or 'unknown'

schema.label: Author Region
schema.description: The region where a story author's Current City is located. Can be a state, province or other region type

schema.label: Author Relationship Status
schema.description: One of 'single', 'relationship', 'engaged', 'married' or 'unknown'

schema.label: Author Type
schema.description: Breakdown of stories created by people vs. Pages

schema.label: Story Language
schema.description: The language in which a story is written

schema.label: Story Links
schema.description: links included in stories

schema.label: Actions
schema.description: Actions like Feeling or Watching which people tag in Facebook stories

schema.label: Action Objects
schema.description: The object of an action in a Facebook story. For example: 'drinking Starbucks', 'drinking' is the activity and 'Starbucks' is the object

schema.label: Parent Author Age
schema.description: Engagements by age of the author of their parent stories

schema.label: Parent Author Country
schema.description: Engagements by country of the author of their parent stories

schema.label: Parent Author Gender
schema.description: Engagements by gender of the authors of their parent stories

schema.label: Parent Author Education
schema.description: Engagements by education level of the authors of their parent stories

schema.label: Parent Author Region
schema.description: Engagements by region of the author of their parent stories

schema.label: Parent Author Relationship Status
schema.description: Engagements by relationship status of the author of their parent stories

schema.label: Engaged Author Type
schema.description: Breakdown of engagements on stories created by people vs. Pages

schema.label: Engaged Hashtags
schema.description: Engagements on stories with hashtags

schema.label: Engaged Languages
schema.description: Engagements on stories by language

schema.label: Engaged Links
schema.description: Engagements on stories containing links

schema.label: Parent Post Type
schema.description: Engagements on stories by media type

schema.label: Engaged Activities
schema.description: Engagements on stories containing Actions

schema.label: Engaged Action Objects
schema.description: Engagements on stories where Action Objects are present

schema.label: Engaged Topic IDs
schema.description: Facebook IDs of topics inferred in stories

schema.label: Engaged Topic Categories
schema.description: a category assigned to a topic, such as 'company' or 'musician/band'

schema.label: Engaged Topics
schema.description: Engagements by Facebook IDs of topics inferred in parent stories

schema.label: Topic IDs
schema.description: Stories by Facebook IDs of inferred topics

schema.label: Topic Category
schema.description: a category assigned to a topic, such as 'company' or 'musician/band'

schema.label: Topic Name
schema.description: Topics inferred in stories

schema.label: Sentiment
schema.description: Sentiment detected in stories; one of 'positive','negative','neutral'

schema.label: Sentiment Engagement
schema.description: Engagements by sentiment detected in parent stories; one of 'positive','negative','neutral'

schema.label: Hashtags
schema.description: Hashtags in stories

schema.label: Story Media Type
schema.description: The media type of a story. One of 'link', 'photo_album', 'note', 'photo', 'post', 'reshare' or 'video'

schema.label: Message Subtype
schema.description: One of 'story', 'comment', 'like' or 'reshare'

schema.label: Message Tags
schema.description: Tags defined in your Filter which are not part of a hierarchical tag structure

schema.label: Links Domain
schema.description: The web domains from which URLs are shared in stories

schema.label: Cleaned URLs
schema.description: URLs shared in stories with UTM codes and anchor tags removed

schema.label: All Links
schema.description: Breakdown of stories with links and their engagements

schema.label: Links Title
schema.description: The titles of links as fetched by Facebook

schema.label: Time
schema.description: Volume of interactions and authors over time
